<p>This repo contains both automated tests for node and manual tests for the browser. The automated tests can be run using mocha (type <code v-pre>mocha</code> in the root directory). To run the manual tests:</p>
<ul>
<li>Build the tests using <code v-pre>build.js</code></li>
<li>Launch the HTTP server (<code v-pre>npm run serve-tests</code>) and visit
<ul>
<li>http://127.0.0.1:1336/amd-test</li>
<li>http://127.0.0.1:1336/browser-test</li>
